bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: Out in the pen today with Rocco the wombat 🐻 Haven’t seen him much since the girls were released, every time I go out there now he’s hit that stage where he flicks the switch as a male wombat 💪 Full territorial mode, wanting to defend his space and own it That’s actually a great sign, he’s well on his way to being ready for the bush 🌿 No interest in humans anymore, does his best to fight us off, and that’s exactly what we want. Hopefully in the next couple of weeks we can get Rocco back out in the wild where he belongs, and free up some room for Betty and Kev Meanwhile, little Steve-O the wombat 🐾 riding in the hoodie pocket is coming along brilliantly. Already such a cheeky little character in the making. Legends all round! ONYA Legends! 💚✨

bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: Spring has finally hit 🌱☀️ Ashlee’s out in the backyard running around with little Steve-O, and he’s even started nibbling on a bit of grass now, good signs for the little bloke 🐾💚 On the downside though, we’ve sadly lost our baby emu with the splayed legs. After a wild windstorm rolled through, we reckon the cage door blew open and he’s either wandered off or, more likely, a bird of prey’s taken him. Doesn’t happen often, but unfortunately it does happen in this game 😔 Poor Amber’s absolutely gutted, she’s walked the farm for hours and checked the cameras, but he’s just vanished into thin air. Tough part of wildlife care… Still, Steve-O’s stoked, and we’ve got to take the positives where we can. ONYA.

bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: Ashlee and Penelope up with the sunrise 🌞 Ashlee’s strolled into the animal hospital with Stephen snuggled up in his little custom nightie 🐾🍼 While we’re topping up the milk powder, it’s the perfect time to let you know the merch is back in stock – including plus sizes 👕💚 Every shirt, hoodie and nightie you grab goes straight back into feeding these little battlers and helping us build the new enclosures and hospital upgrades. Huge thanks to everyone who’s already jumped on board and supported – you’re keeping this dream alive. Onya legends. onyaapparel.shop

bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: First red-bellied black snake catch today 🐍🔥 After the police spotted one hanging out at their handgun training facility, we headed down, scooped him up, and everything went to plan. A couple of k’s down the road I released him into a perfect little swampy area, right where he belongs. He was a little bit fiery when we let him go though — bit upsetting when I’ve taken him out to a beautiful new spot, you’d think he’d have a bit more respect 😅 It’s probably looking like it’s going to be a pretty big snake season too. In the last few days they’ve definitely started becoming more active, waking up from their long winter slumber. They’re all on the move now, looking for a tasty snack to snag 🐸🦎🐍 👉 Fun facts: • Red-bellied black snakes are one of Australia’s most iconic snakes • They are venomous ⚠️ their bite can cause pain, swelling, headaches, nausea and even muscle damage, but thanks to quick medical treatment, fatalities are very rare • They love swampy, moist habitats like creeks, lagoons, and wetlands • They actually eat frogs, small lizards, and even other snakes Beautiful, sleek snakes that play an important role in the ecosystem. Always a thrill to see one up close, and even better to give him a safe new home 🌿 ONYA!

bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: Ashlee and Amber out exercising their little critters this morning 💚 Ashlee’s got the wombats, Amber’s got the kangaroos, and they’re all out in the orchard on little adventures 🐻🦘 Such awesome bonding moments to see. I feel a bit left out though… might have to find myself an emu as a spirit animal and join in next time 🐦😂 How good’s this? Except for Kev, of course. He’s not doing any running around, he’s parked on the lawn eating all the best grass. Fat little wombat, aren’t ya Kev? 🍃 Onya legends 🙌 #ONYA #WildlifeRescue #WombatWarrior #KangarooCare #FamilyAndCritters

bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: WARNING ‼️ NOT A HAPPY ENDING.. After footy training I got a call just up the road 🚗💥🐇 A young girl, only a couple of days on her license, had no fault of her own when a kangaroo came bounding out of the bush right on the apex of a hill. Sadly she collided with it and completely wrote her car off. She’s very lucky she wasn’t injured. Kangaroos are everywhere in my area and accidents like this happen often. At first the roo didn’t look too bad and I had some hope, but once I stood it up I could see its hip was completely smashed. The call had to be made to put it down 💔 That’s the reality of these jobs – not many happy endings when big kangaroos meet cars, usually both sides come off badly. The damage to the car was considerable, a real reminder of just how dangerous these situations are. Not a great story, but I share both the good and the bad, and this was one of the sad ones. But a good reminder of the risks for people especially new drivers of of Australian country roads, be safe these people did a awesome job in handling the whole situation ❤️At the end you’ll see me tell one of our little joeys to promise me they’ll stay off the road – nothing but mischief out there for them. Onya legends 💚 #ONYA #WildlifeRescue #Kangaroo #RoadSafety

bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: Just a little update on Braxton 🐻💚 our young orphaned wombat. He came into care after his mum was sadly shot in a paddock. A farmer found him and brought him in, but by then he was already at that tricky age where they’re much harder to hand raise. Braxton’s a very cranky little boy, full of stress and not keen on humans, which makes it tough to build trust and get the weight on him. But he’s slowly improving, step by step, and we’re doing our best to help him along. It’s not always easy when they come in older like this, but every bit of progress is a win. He’s still grumpy, but he’s our little Braxton, and he’s getting there. Onya 💚 #ONYA #WombatWarrior #WildlifeRescue #BraxtonTheWombat

video_name: Day 3 and I’m already a city boy. I rode the subway, conquered the metra, and even made a new best friend who’s about three times my size. We wrestled, we ran, and then I crashed. I was out cold on the train, snoring while strangers laughed. My secret weapon? The gym bag. Forget cars, forget kennels — carry me like your lunch and I’ll curl up happy. I’ll even climb in when we’re not going anywhere, just to snooze. City adventures, big friends, bag naps. Foster life looks good on me. Available @Chicago Canine Rescue  #adoptdontshop #fosterdog #pittiemix

video_name: They call me Capris. I’m allergic to personal space. I’m 8 months old, part pittie, part shadow, and recently found myself back at animal control with a broken toe and a sniffly nose. Luckily, I landed in my first foster home. Day one? Easy. I sniffed everything, claimed my kennel, and then glued myself to my foster human. I love toys, treats, and stuffies. I even rocked an elephant costume on my first day like it was no big deal. And when I wake up, I make grunts that sound like a tiny piglet — because mornings are hard. I’m sweet, snuggly, and more than ready for forever. Available @Chicago Canine Rescue  #adoptdontshop #fosterdog #pittiemix

video_name: They call me Sweater Weather. I was found in the back of a U-Haul. I’m five years old, and let’s just say my track record with humans hasn’t been the best. But I know the right person is out there for me. I’m a bully mix wrecking ball with zoomies that turn into backyard parkour. Picnic tables, fences, lawn chairs… your boy’s clearing them like an Olympic athlete. Graceful? Not always. Entertaining? Every time. What I need is a home with someone who knows how to handle big energy and bigger love. You give me a chance, I’ll give you loyalty, laughs, and the best crash-landings you’ve ever seen. Abailable @Chicago Canine Rescue  #adoptdontshop #shelterdog #bullymix

video_name: I don’t work for free. If you want tricks out of me, you better sweet talk first. It’s day two in my foster home and I’m already getting comfy. I’ve picked out my favorite snooze spots, and I take my gardening duties outside very seriously. Mealtime? That’s my toughest test. I have to sit there and resist, sometimes I can’t even look at my bowl until I get the okay. By the end of the night, I’m out cold — stuffy in my mouth, tucked into my crate, dreaming of tomorrow. Available @Chicago Canine Rescue  #adoptdontshop #fosterdog #pittiemix

video_name: Okay I messed up. It’s day 4 and I pooped my pants. I got a bath. My kennel got scrubbed. I gave my best “sorry and thank you” face. My tummy’s been upset, but foster dad’s got me on meds and chicken-and-rice to help me feel better. While I napped, he went to take pictures of other shelter dogs. I didn’t know where he went… but I was so happy when he came back. By bedtime I claimed the couch instead of going upstairs. Foster life is exhausting, but I think I’m getting the hang of it. Featured Pups: @OTAT  Capri: @Chicago Canine Rescue

video_name: My foster dad promised me I’ll never end up in the shelter again. It’s Day 5 in my foster home and things are looking up. My tummy’s finally settling, my walks are getting easier, and I’m starting to feel more comfortable in the neighborhood. I even made a new friend today—gave her a good ear sniff for approval. When I’m not on neighborhood watch duty, you’ll find me stretched out, dreaming away, and enjoying this new chapter. Available @Chicago Canine Rescue

video_name: Hi, I’m Labubu. I was in line to be returned to animal control when a shelter worker saved me. I look a little scraggly right now, I have a part time snaggletooth, and nobody knows what breed I am. But here’s what you do need to know: I’ve got lightening fast chompers, I’m gentle but goofy, and I’ll keep you laughing every single day. I may not be the type to fall head-over-heels right away, but I’m loyal, quirky, and full of character. All I need now is a bath, some love, and a forever family who sees the charm in a little gremlin like me. Available @Chicago Canine Rescue  Bandana @Pink Tongue Dog Bandanas  #adoptdontshop #shelterdog #chicagodog

Great stories found here 👇🏼
video_name: Why do adoption fees exist? Every adoption fee supports the shelter. That includes paying rent, staff, food, daily care, and most of all, medical bills. But the truth is, adoption fees barely make a dent. They’re more of a symbolic donation when a dog goes home. The real lifeline comes from community donations and ongoing support. At the start of this year, three dogs at @Chicago Canine Rescue cost nearly $30,000 in medical care. That’s an impossible number for a small shelter without help from the people who care. Adoption fees help, but in reality it’s the community support that keeps the shelter running and gives these dogs a second chance. Follow @4evertails to see more behind the scenes stories and how you can help make an impact!

video_name: 📚 Как мы учились в Турции: путь Тоси от 4 до (почти) 9 Когда мы переехали в Турцию — Тосе было 4. И с этого началось большое путешествие по школам, системам, садикам и… вшам 😂 ⸻ 🔸 2021 год 4 года. Частный турецкий садик. Языка нет — и у неё, и у меня 🫠 Но дети есть дети: через пару месяцев она уже «чирикала» на турецком так, что мне самой было интересно послушать. ⸻ 🔸 2021–2022 5 лет — в Турции это уже подготовительный класс. 0 класс в частной школе. За год — 5 раз вши за год. Покинули с достоинством и без вшей😅 ⸻ 🔸 2022–2024 6 и 7 лет. Пошли в другую частную турецкую школу. Выдержали 2 класса. Сколько будет 9 + 3 — не знаем. Зато турецкий уже щебечет, как настоящая турчанка 💪 ⸻ 🔸 2024–2025 Формально — снова 2 класс. Но по русской системе она как раз по возрасту. Решаем: онлайн-обучение в Фоксфорде + летом с репетитором закрываем 1 класс. Для социализации — коворкинг. По факту: учим, понимаем, но только если «сидеть сверху» 😅 Отвлекается, ругаемся, пересматриваем уроки, которые и так короткие. Мама иногда в шоке😅 ⸻ 🔸 2025–2026 Идём в 3 класс русской школы в Анталии. Учителя, парты, доска, расписание — всё как в моём детстве. В Анталии всего 2 русские школы, выдающие дипломы, и связанные с турецкой системой. Выбрали Московскую в Ларе — по атмосфере, подходу, ощущениям. Если приживёмся — переезжаем ближе к школе. Да, опять переезд 😂

video_name: O resgate da Julieta e Haru foi o mais impressionante para nós.  Em questão de 1 semana tosamos a Juju, demos banho, castramos ela e logo em seguida fizemos o mesmo com seu melhor amigo Haru.  Apesar de os 2 terem tutor na época, a dona não pensou duas vezes em nos passar a responsabilidade de cuidar deles, já que a mesma não tinha condições.  Em menos de 1 semana, Julieta e Haru tiveram suas vidas transformadas. Ficaram limpinhos, castrados, medicados, cuidados, bem alimentados e 7 dias depois, tiveram um encontro de alma com sua verdadeira família.  Hoje, Juju e Haru vivem como 2 príncipes, em um lar cheio de amor. Não passam mais fome, não dormem mais na rua, muito pelo contrário, tem tudo do bom e do melhor.  Me emociono sempre que vejo uma foto ou vídeo deles vivendo essa vida maravilhosa que eles tem hoje na casa nova! Somos gratos a Deus por nos usar como instrumento na vida dessas criaturas tão preciosas. Jesus, estamos ao Seu dispor!  Vote no Will para o Prêmio iBest ❤️ Seu voto e apoio é muito importante e nos ajuda demais!  O link para votar está na minha bio 🙏 #cachorros #cachorro #cachorrosdotiktok #poodle #viralata

Buscamos os dois juntos em Minas Gerais na cidade de um colega de trabalho do Diego, pois a mãezinha deles havia dado cria a 8 filhotinhos.  Will e Iron se viam sempre que dava. Um posava na casa do outro já que Iron foi adotado por um casal da nossa cidade.  Até que perdemos esse costume deles se encontrarem.  Depois desse afastamento, Will ficou por mais de 3 anos sem ter um melhor amigo cachorro para brincar. Até que a Clarinha chegou.  Will e Claramela tem a mesma conexão de Will e Iron. E até na cor caramelo os dois se parecem.  Atualmente Iron está bem. Enorme. Ele é a cara do pai deles que é um Pit Monster.  Mesmo tendo adotado a Clara já adulta, na minha visão, ela e o Will sempre serão duas crianças. Meus bebês ❤️ #cachorros #cachorro #pitbull #filhote #filhotes

video_name: Un perro no es un objeto, es una vida 🐾 Hoy queremos compartir una realidad triste que nos duele.. Berlin solo era un bebe cuando encontró lo que creíamos sería su hogar para siempre. Sin embargo, hoy nos lo devolvieron. Un perro no es un regalo, ni un pasatiempo, ni algo que se pueda "probar" y luego descartar. Es un ser vivo que siente, que confía, que se entrega con todo su corazón. Cada adopción debe ser una decisión consciente y responsable, porque detrás de cada abandono hay un animal que sufre, que no entiende por qué lo dejaron de querer. Pedimos que quienes decidan adoptar lo hagan sabiendo que se trata de un compromiso de por vida: en las buenas y en las malas, con paciencia, con respeto y con amor. Adoptar es cambiar una vida para siempre. 🐶 #labachimanada #amor #perros #adoptanocompres

video_name: There is a way you go about things. Never interacting with specific  creators , copying their personality , aesthetic, lyrics , buying the same exact props they use in their videos , never showing them love on their videos , and then going and putting their name in a song for clout is NOT the way to do it.  Is there space for everyone YES, should you have your own style and personality YES. Should you copy other people in the same space as you, NO!  Am I the only one doing what I’m doing NO , but PLEASE don’t down right copy. People see what works for me and my audience so they watch , copy and then mention my name in their song because they KNOW the fans will react a certain way . That’s not love that is mockery and it’s not okay. Because IF the love was genuine they would be interacting with me not watching and copying . I have 4 different songs / free styles where I say “I sing I rap I hoop , I teach. “ I have MULTIPLE different songs where I say I teach babies how to speak / talk .” I have SEVERAL videos of me hooping dating back past 2023 . I’ve BEEN doing this. So to have my name mentioned in a video of a person using extremely similar lyrics and hooping in the video is disturbing and it’s basically taunting me.  I’m not the only person this creator has copied they also copied someone else all the way down to the same outfit and headwear . So I’m not the only one this is happening to in this situation . Share the space YES , Be inspired YES, Copy NO.  And NO I’m not hating on anyone , I’m speaking facts . The viewers don’t see it from the lense I see it in and that’s fine .  I’m going to leave you with this: they shouted out 5 major black female kid yt creators in their song , but follow NONE of the people they shouted out . They follow a ton of other kid yt creators but didn’t shout them out in the song .  So was it showing love or was it calculated to get a reaction out of our fans to make it appear that they support . And that’s a rhetorical question . #mshouston #freestyle

video_name: 📌 Detail fakta: Nama: Pemasangan Sepatu Kuda Sumber Video: Zack D Films Lokasi: Digunakan secara global, terutama di negara dengan tradisi berkuda Tahun: Sudah dilakukan sejak lebih dari 1.000 tahun lalu Status: Fakta yang tercatat Banyak orang mengira kalau kuda merasa kesakitan saat dipasangkan sepatu kuda dengan paku, karena terlihat seperti kukunya dipaku langsung. Padahal, kenyataannya tidak begitu. Kuku kuda terbuat dari keratin, bahan yang sama dengan kuku dan rambut manusia. Bagian luar kuku kuda tidak memiliki saraf, sehingga ketika dipaku dengan benar, kuda sama sekali tidak merasa sakit. Proses pemasangan sepatu kuda dilakukan oleh seorang ahli yang disebut farrier. Mereka sangat terlatih untuk tahu bagian mana yang aman dipaku dan ukuran sepatu yang sesuai. Sepatu kuda ini tidak hanya sebagai aksesoris, tetapi berfungsi penting untuk melindungi kuku dari kerusakan, terutama bagi kuda yang sering berjalan di permukaan keras atau kasar. Kalau sepatu kuda dipasang sembarangan, memang bisa menyebabkan masalah, seperti pincang atau kuku yang rusak. Itulah kenapa perawatan kuku kuda rutin dilakukan, termasuk pemotongan kuku berlebih dan penggantian sepatu yang sudah aus. Bagi kuda pekerja atau kuda balap, sepatu kuda jadi bagian vital agar tetap sehat dan kuat. Tradisi ini sudah berlangsung lebih dari seribu tahun. Bukti arkeologis menunjukkan bahwa orang-orang Eropa pada abad pertengahan sudah menggunakan bentuk awal sepatu kuda untuk melindungi hewan tunggangan mereka. Seiring waktu, teknik dan material sepatu kuda makin berkembang, tetapi prinsip utamanya tetap sama, yaitu menjaga kuku tetap sehat tanpa menyakiti hewan. Hingga kini, pemasangan sepatu kuda masih sering jadi salah satu hal yang bikin orang penasaran. Ternyata, rahasianya sederhana, karena kuku kuda mirip dengan kuku manusia, maka selama dipasang dengan benar, mereka sama sekali tidak merasa sakit. #faktaunik #hewan #fakebodyy⚠️  #sejarahdunia #funfact

Proses ini tentu mustahil, karena berat satu benua saja setara dengan miliaran ton batuan yang tertanam dalam lempeng bumi. Tapi dalam imajinasi liar, tugboat raksasa itu cukup kuat untuk menggeser lempeng-lempeng tektonik ke arah yang sama. Benturan itu sekaligus berperan sebagai “palunya” alam semesta, menutup celah yang memisahkan benua-benua tersebut. Air laut pun masuk jadi faktor penting. Komponen kecil yang terletak di sistem pembuangan itu mengandung logam seperti platina, paladium, dan rodium yang harganya melonjak di pasar scrap, sehingga menjadi incaran pencuri. Dampaknya bukan cuma biaya perbaikan yang mahal, tapi juga gangguan dokumen asuransi, hilangnya kendaraan sementara, dan rasa tidak aman bagi pemilik mobil. Kisah yang sering terulang di berita lokal biasanya mirip: korban pulang ke mobil dan mendapati suara knalpot aneh, atau konverter hilang begitu saja dari parkiran. Bagi banyak orang, momen itu terasa seperti dilecehkan secara ekonomi, karena perbaikan bisa menghabiskan ribuan dolar dan sering memakan waktu. Di komunitas pemilik mobil, kemarahan dan kreativitas bereaksi dengan cepat, muncul berbagai taktik pencegahan dari yang sederhana sampai yang lebih teknis. Beberapa langkah pencegahan populer memang mulai dipakai luas, misalnya memarkir di garasi, memilih area parkir terang dan ramai, memasang pelindung fisik yang sesuai standar, atau menandai komponen dengan nomor plat kendaraan supaya rongsokan enggan menerima barang yang jelas-jelas curian. Ada juga inisiatif komunitas dimana tetangga saling mengawasi parkiran dan berbagi informasi. Namun tidak ada langkah tunggal yang sempurna, sehingga kombinasi tindakan pencegahan dan lapor cepat ke pihak berwajib tetap kunci. Di sisi penegakan hukum, beberapa yurisdiksi memperketat aturan jual-beli scrap dan memperkenalkan regulasi yang meminta identifikasi penjual serta bukti kepemilikan. Kampanye kesadaran publik juga gencar dijalankan, karena banyak pemilik belum tahu seberapa mudah konverter bisa diambil dan seberapa mahal akibatnya. Industri aftermarket juga merespon dengan solusi proteksi yang lebih baik, sekaligus edukasi tentang apa yang boleh dan tidak boleh dilakukan supaya tidak melanggar hukum atau membahayakan kendaraan. Intinya, ini masalah nyata yang menggabungkan motif ekonomi kriminal dan kerentanan teknologi kendaraan modern. Untuk pemilik mobil, kewaspadaan adalah investasi: parkir aman, dokumentasi lengkap, dan bila perlu konsultasi dengan bengkel resmi untuk opsi proteksi yang sesuai tipe kendaraan. Dan untuk publik luas, memahami bagaimana pasar scrap bekerja membantu menjelaskan kenapa komponen kecil itu jadi target, sehingga solusi yang efektif perlu melibatkan produsen, regulator, penegak hukum, dan masyarakat. #faktaunik #fakesituation  #edukasi  #fakesituation⚠️  #fakebodyy⚠️

Rahasia terbesar ada pada palang yang digunakan. Alih-alih memakai palang biasa, mereka memasang palang yang bisa berputar. Artinya, ketika seseorang menggenggamnya, genggaman itu akan terus berubah posisi. Otot tangan akan cepat lelah, gesekan akan membuat telapak sakit, dan semakin lama akan terasa mustahil untuk bertahan. Palang yang tampak sepele itu menjadi musuh tak terlihat yang membuat banyak peserta menyerah sebelum waktu habis. Belum cukup sampai di situ, sering kali ada trik tambahan yang bikin peserta makin sulit. Beberapa penjaga karnaval diketahui sengaja menggoyang palang atau membuat gerakan kecil yang mengganggu keseimbangan. Seolah-olah permainan ini adil, padahal sebenarnya sudah dimanipulasi sejak awal. Bukannya hadiah, kebanyakan peserta hanya pulang dengan tangan merah, lecet, dan perasaan kecewa. Meski begitu, permainan ini tetap populer. Banyak yang tertarik mencoba karena hadiah yang dipajang di depan mata, biasanya berupa uang tunai, boneka raksasa, atau barang elektronik. Ada pula orang yang sudah tahu rahasianya tapi tetap mencoba demi gengsi atau sekadar tantangan. Sensasi beradu dengan trik tersembunyi itu justru menambah daya tarik permainan, meski peluang menang sangat kecil. Kisah tentang “Hang Challenge” kemudian jadi bahan viral di media sosial. Orang-orang berbagi pengalaman gagal, menunjukkan telapak tangan penuh lecet, atau sekadar memperingatkan bahwa permainan itu hampir mustahil dimenangkan. Hingga sekarang, ia tetap jadi salah satu contoh klasik bagaimana permainan karnaval sering kali diatur supaya keuntungan tetap berada di pihak penyelenggara. Bagi sebagian orang, ini bukan sekadar permainan, melainkan simbol betapa mudahnya manusia terkecoh oleh sesuatu yang tampak sederhana. #faktaunik #fakesituation⚠️  #darkhistory #kisahnyata #fakebodyy⚠️

Kebanyakan orang berpikir cara terbaik adalah lompat ke depan mengikuti arah truk. Padahal, kalau kamu lompat ke depan, tubuhmu justru masih punya momentum tambahan. Akibatnya, kamu menghantam tanah dengan kecepatan yang lebih besar dari kecepatan truk itu sendiri. Dampaknya bisa fatal, mulai dari kaki patah, terkilir, bahkan cedera serius di kepala. Cara yang lebih aman adalah melompat ke arah berlawanan, yaitu ke belakang. Dengan menghadap ke belakang lalu mendorong tubuh keluar, kamu justru mengurangi momentum kecepatanmu. Gerakan ini semacam “meng-cancel” sebagian kecepatan truk, sehingga saat menyentuh tanah, lajumu lebih lambat dibanding kalau lompat ke depan. Inilah alasan kenapa mendarat mundur punya kemungkinan lebih kecil untuk bikin cedera parah. Setelah mendarat, jangan langsung coba berdiri tegak. Biarkan tubuhmu berguling untuk menyebarkan energi benturan ke seluruh badan, bukan hanya satu bagian tubuh. Teknik ini mirip dengan cara atlet parkour atau prajurit terlatih saat melompat dari ketinggian. Gulungan tubuh membantu memperlambat momentum dengan lebih aman. Meski begitu, melompat dari kendaraan bergerak tetap berisiko tinggi. Faktor kecepatan, permukaan tanah, dan kondisi tubuh sangat berpengaruh. Pada truk yang melaju sangat cepat, bahkan melompat mundur pun bisa tetap berbahaya. Itulah sebabnya, teknik ini lebih ke prinsip fisika sederhana yang menunjukkan bagaimana arah momentum bekerja, bukan saran praktis untuk dicoba sembarangan. Kisah ini mengingatkan kita bahwa terkadang logika insting manusia bisa menipu. Alih-alih mengikuti naluri untuk lompat ke depan, justru arah sebaliknya yang lebih aman. Prinsip fisika sederhana ini bisa jadi pengetahuan tambahan yang unik tentang bagaimana tubuh manusia bereaksi terhadap kecepatan dan momentum. #faktaunik #fakesituation  #fakebodyy⚠️  #fakesituation⚠️  #lifehacks

Saat semangka mulai masuk, ia langsung menekan trakea, menutup jalan napas, dan membuat orang tersebut tidak bisa bernapas sama sekali. Benda keras sebesar itu juga akan merobek jaringan halus di kerongkongan, menyebabkan perdarahan serius dan rasa sakit yang luar biasa. Andaikan semangka itu bisa masuk lebih dalam, ia akan menghantam rongga dada. Paru-paru akan tertekan hingga kolaps, jantung terjepit, dan aliran darah terganggu. Bahkan jika secara ajaib bisa sampai ke perut, ukuran semangka tetap terlalu besar. Lambung manusia hanya mampu menampung sekitar 1,5 liter makanan, sementara semangka utuh bisa puluhan kali lipat lebih besar. Hal ini akan membuat lambung pecah dan organ dalam hancur. Usaha muntah paksa pun hanya akan memperparah luka yang sudah ada, dengan risiko robeknya kerongkongan atau pembuluh darah utama. Dalam kondisi nyata, seseorang yang mencoba ini pasti langsung membutuhkan pertolongan medis darurat, dan peluang bertahan hidup hampir tidak ada. Eksperimen semacam ini memang tidak pernah benar-benar dilakukan, melainkan hanya ilustrasi ekstrem untuk menunjukkan keterbatasan tubuh manusia. Ide ini sering muncul sebagai hiburan atau teori liar, tetapi secara ilmiah jelas mustahil dilakukan tanpa mengorbankan nyawa. bio: An ongoing conversation. Using fiction to tell the truth.
video_name: What if I told you that the technology making this very post possible exists precisely because of the principles behind DEI?  The narrative that Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion initiatives lower standards is not just incorrect—it's a perspective that ignores the very foundation of modern innovation. This video powerfully counters that myth by highlighting the monumental contributions of Black scientists and inventors. From Dr. Shirley Jackson's research enabling fiber optics and call waiting to Dr. Marian Croak's patents which make internet video possible, their work is integral to our daily lives and global economy. We explore the legacies of Garrett Morgan (traffic lights), Dr. Charles Drew (blood banks), and Katherine Johnson (space exploration), among others. DEI is not about lowering the bar; it's about removing systemic barriers so that talent and genius can be recognized and cultivated regardless of background. It is a strategic imperative for business growth and technological progress.  When we exclude diverse perspectives, we don't just risk missing out on the next great invention—we actively stifle the potential for breakthroughs that benefit everyone. The question isn't whether these individuals deserved a seat at the table. Of course they do. The question is, can we afford to keep building a future without the full spectrum of talent in the room? Watch the video to understand the true, innovation-driven purpose of DEI. #DEI #Innovation #Leadership #BusinessStrategy #BlackExcellence

bio: An ongoing conversation. Using fiction to tell the truth.
video_name: I am autistic, with multiple disabilities. I'm trans/non-binary, and I am exhausted.  I'm on the front lines of this fight, not because I enlisted, but because my communities were the invasion point.   All day I defend against attacks, left flank, right flank and center. I, and my community, defend not only our flanks, but yours.  The most damaging barrage both to the cause and to morale are those that come from behind-friendly fire.  Most people are aware of the vitriol and hate that comes against the Trans community, even from the supposed left.  But few are even aware of the unending onslaught of ableist attacks that- while aimed at the enemy- strike us in the disabled community with equal force.  Many argue against the wild medical claims. They use the same harmful rhetoric though to describe us. They infantalize us, paint our lives as tragedies and burdens.  I'm not always the most gentle with our allies.   I sometimes return friendly fire because it becomes hard to distinguish even in designated safe zones, who is really an ally and who is an unwitting conspirator.  While some of you have just joined this fight, remember those of us who have been in it for years, decades, and lifetimes.  Do not be surprised when we fire back in self-defense. We can only identify you as an ally if you cease fire, unlearn your ableism and offer aid instead.

video_name: وابشركم ٣ الى ٤ مشهورات ما التزمو وراح تسحب رخصهم اليوم أو بكره 🙏 القرارات الجديده من هيئة تنظيم الإعلام  - كل محتوى من شأنه التنمر على الآخرين أو الاستهزاء بهم. - كل محتوى من شأنه إظهار خصوصيات الأسرة وخلافاتها الداخلية. - كل محتوى يتم من خلاله تصوير الأطفال أو العمالة كمحتوى يومي بأي شكل من الأشكال وسواء بطريقة إيجابية أو سلبية - كل محتوى يتضمن معلومات مضللة أو غير صحيحة. - كل محتوى يتضمن لغة مبتذلة، أو تباهي بالأموال، أو السيارات، أو أي ممتلكات شخصية، أو عمالة أو التباهي بالنسب والقبيلة والمناطقية. - كل ما من شأنه إثارة التنابز بالألقاب، أو القبلية، أو العنصرية، أو الطائفية. - كل محتوى من شأنه عكس صورة سلبية عن القيم الاجتماعية والوطنية. *محددات اللباس غير المحتشم* والذي يتعارض مع قيم المجتمع وجودة المحتوى، هي: - كل لباس يظهر الجسد من الكتفين والصدر إلى الساقين. - كل لباس ضيق يبرز معالم الجسد. - كل لباس شفاف يخالف الآداب العامة ويتعارض مع القيم السائدة.

video_name: Falamos sobre um verme assustador que pode viver dentro de você por anos, chegando a mais de dez metros de comprimento e só saindo quando você vê pedaços dele nas suas fezes. Esse parasita entra no corpo pelo que comemos, como carne mal passada ou comida contaminada, e suga todos os seus nutrientes, deixando você fraco. Muitas pessoas não sentem nada, mas os sinais mais comuns são dor abdominal, emagrecimento rápido e até pedaços do verme aparecendo no vaso sanitário. Alguns casos extremos envolvem vermes de quase dois metros saindo do corpo, como o de um homem que adorava comer sashimi de salmão cru todos os dias. O mais assustador é que esses vermes podem viver por até trinta anos dentro de uma pessoa, crescendo cada vez mais. #vermedafita #parasita #sashimicru #intestino #fezes

video_name: Alessandro Venier: aggiornamenti sul possibile movente e sul passato dell’uomo. Dalle prime indagini su di lui e sulla sua famiglia, è emerso che Alessandro era un ragazzo problematico fin da bambino. Il rapporto con sua madre e con la sua compagna è stato definito come “burrascoso”, senza entrare però in troppi dettagli. La cosa certa è che Lorena Venier, sua madre, ha dichiarato che il figlio era violento nei confronti della sua compagna; il che, le avrebbe spinte ad agire in questa maniera.  Tornando al passato di Alessandro, si sa che su di lui pendeva una condanna che stava per diventare esecutiva e che gli avrebbe impedito l’espatrio. La causa? Una serie di piccoli reati commessi in passato e in tempi diversi. Questo è il motivo per cui aveva in programma di trasferirsi in Colombia con la sua compagna e sua figlia il prima possibile. Tra i reati, lesioni personali gravi, coltivazione di sostanze illecite e attività non autorizzate di recupero di residuati bellici.  Alle superiori gli era stato contestato il reato di procurato allarme e quello di minacce. E più tardi sarebbe stato protagonista anche di un episodio violento nei confronti di un ex collega. Ma si parla anche maltrattamenti di animali e numerosi atti di esibizionismo. Per ultimo, ma non per importanza, è da sottolineare che i maltrattamenti su sua madre e sulla sua compagna erano sempre più frequenti, e i carabinieri erano anche intervenuti più volte. Ora restano da accertare le dinamiche familiari, il reale movente e le accuse contro le due donne. Quando ci saranno aggiornamenti vi racconterò tutto!
